{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278030, "create_time": 1657104589, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "个人认为应该用以下三点措施改善氛围：\n1. 停用临时账号，临时账号的存在已经没有任何积极意义。由于临时账号还可以回复树洞，有些人好奇内容取消了默认屏蔽，结果卡大佐看到用临时账号发还会有人看，进了里世界之后又持续用临时账号贴大字报，输出精神污染。\n2. 改进举报机制，十次举报自动删除＋禁言\n3. 完善折叠机制，对于不折叠或者不规范折叠的树洞，如果三个人以上要求打同样的折叠警告，就自动添加上zzxg、xxg等对应的默认屏蔽的折叠警告", "timestamp": 1657104589}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278032, "create_time": 1657104651, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "劝退新人就怎么了，树洞难道是靠流量挣钱的吗", "timestamp": 1657104651}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278033, "create_time": 1657104687, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "如何界定是否zzxg", "timestamp": 1657104687}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278035, "create_time": 1657104765, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "什么是“正常的校内讨论平台”", "timestamp": 1657104765}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278036, "create_time": 1657104782, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "树洞为什么要像一个“正常的校内讨论平台”", "timestamp": 1657104782}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278038, "create_time": 1657104876, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我自己从未参与过dz给的截图这样的讨论，但是觉得看着还挺乐呵的；有时候看到自己不喜欢的发言，我会通过屏蔽和拉黑的方式处理，或者评论自己为什么不喜欢这个发言", "timestamp": 1657104876}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 278039, "create_time": 1657104877, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 如果变成了魔怔人自嗨的树洞，除了魔